text:
Howdy beautiful people,  <!channel>

Welcome back to fall 2023 for those still studying!!! You’re a star!!

Fun reminders:
1. Hike with Zvi on Sat Sept 2, 2023. That’s next weekend. If you’re not on the list and want to, let me know with a :hiking_boot: 
    a. Right now we have a confirmed via outlook <@U03UM07E4D8> <@U04HVDA1022> with tentative <@U02MANZL55F> <@U0495G3QQ1W> and previous confirmation from previous post <@U04S6L1NS9M> <@U01JYRB9DL2> <@U02BQJX5TB8> (if any of this has changed let me know)
2. Camping trip ------ looks like there was a tie so please break it and when we do, I’ll send ya’ll with 2-3 air bnbs to vote on and split via Venmo or Zelle that cost within reason.
    a. Aug 27 (this weekend)  <@U0495G3QQ1W> <@U02UAQKR56C> <@U04185JLG8M> <@U04S6L1NS9M>|| <@U040WB5GXRV> <@U01N1775WSU>  :one:
    b. Sept 10 (second weekend in Sept) <@U0495G3QQ1W> <@U02UAQKR56C> <@U04185JLG8M> <@U04S6L1NS9M> || <@U0417UDBBUM> <@U04184BSKM3>  :two:
    c. Tie breakers: <@U02MANZL55F> <@U01N1775WSU> <@U0495G3QQ1W> <@U02UAQKR56C> <@U04185JLG8M> <@U04S6L1NS9M>
_Free_ tickets coming up if you like GT football…………thanks to our one and only Dr. <@U02EYBE4QNA> !!! :raised_hands:
Tell me if you want a seat--*first come first serve*, so comment in thread if you want a certain date/game and I’ll go by that.

I have 2 stands tickets *home* games (which is bleacher stadium seating) :
~9/9      South Carolina State (2/2~ <@U02UAQKR56C> <@U0495G3QQ1W>)
~9/30    Bowling Green*~ (~4/4~ <@U02DD5VQLBV> <@U02UAQKR56C> <@U040V1EQYMS> <@U041DBXGPC4>) + 2/2 (<@U0577EXET0F> <@U04HVDA1022>)
10/21  Boston College (1/2 <@U04184BSKM3>)
10/28  North Carolina
~11/18 Syracuse (2/2)~
11/25 Georgia (1/2 <@U03UBDM3BE2>)
*Bowling Green game (9/30) will be additional 4 CoC suite seats (the VIP kind!)
……..I might go to the 9/30 one just to see a game without stepping on toes. I would go to the Georgia one but last time we got creamed so hard. Either way let me know!

PS I hope ya’ll had fun at Battle and Brew for those who went!!!!

PPS for those hoping to go to six flags in September, the tickets are out!! And at least 2-3 students are going!! Linked above by <@U01N1775WSU>. Thanks for linking us!!

And lastly, to the flier Ana posted above this…..anybody graduatingMay 2024??????? Can we walk together?! :heart_hands::skin-tone-3:

See your faces very soon!
Cherie Lum
